add_indexed_columns.Rd

This step uses the dataframe indices to index every payment and every reserve to the index year.

This function resembles only step 4 of the data preparation process, see description in details of prepare_data()

Usage

add_indexed_columns(extended_claims_data, indices)

Arguments

extended_claims_data

dataframe after step 3, see details of prepare_data().

indices

dataframe, see details of prepare_data().

Value
